mat": "2 - 640x1136"}, {"format_id": "dash-876166268310859v", "ext": "mp4", "width": 720, "height": 1280, "tbr": 967.852, "format_note": "DASH video", "container": "mp4_dash", "vcodec": "avc1.64001f", "acodec": "none", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQN9mI33kYUbACrCUc2u2f4x5lEpKOoOCDM6_LexP-aATBEFaOq9g13FQ8AzjwHpx-OaiPlaTxgK9QDddgVNggJBj3ULX0Jo0wuKsZI.mp4?_nc_cat=109&_nc_sid=9ca052&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=s5jNzD0Fu-YQ7kNvwG5Vonl&&ccb=17-1&_nc_gid=Qwb7EL13Er77pCLI8_Piww&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ss=7a32e&oh=00_Af3QadwOP7Lw5QHGcR7WmLpoHd5m97t4KsF4pgOdmU1Wxg&oe=69D0E716", "manifest_stream_number": 0, "is_dash_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 967.852, "resolution": "720x1280", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 18346602, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-876166268310859v - 720x1280 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by expansionwithdrjess", "description": "Most people think manifestation is about what you want.\n\nIt’s not. It’s about who your nervous system thinks you are.\n\nAnd that identity was formed long before you ever chose it. When you were little, your brain lived in a highly programmable state.\n\nYou absorbed tone, chaos, pressure, roles, expectations…\nand your body built an identity around whatever felt safest.\nThe strong one.\nThe invisible one.\nThe caretaker.\nThe perfectionist.\nThe one who doesn’t need anything.\nThe one who earns love by overfunctioning.\nThat isn’t personality. That’s survival coding.\n\nAnd here’s the kicker:\nYour nervous system will recreate ANY reality that matches that identity.\n\nNot because you’re sabotaging yourself,\nbut because your body is loyal to whatever once kept you alive.\n\nIf you want a new reality, you don’t need more affirmations.\n\nYou need a new identity.\n\n👇 Tell me in the comments:\nWhich survival identity do YOU resonate with?\nThe strong one, the pleaser, the perfectionist, the invisible one, or something else entirely?\n\n✨ Follow for Part 3: Why Your Nervous System Doesn’t Believe Your Affirmations.", "duration": 151.648, "timestamp": 1764861866, "uploader_id": "62459480873", "uploader": "Dr. Jess | Nervous System + Identity", "channel": "expansionwithdrjess", "like_count": 10774, "comment_count": 254, "comments": [{"author": "paological.fit", "author_id": "74800685654", "id": "18110381554770472", "text": "Heart this for me to hear this again and again, please.", "timestamp": 1774985155}, {"author": "dangerella95", "author_id": "58867415629", "id": "17856777867683764", "text": "The kobe study. Kobe Bean Bryant became black mamba and his game changed. Well said ma’am. You are 1000‰ on target no miss no 🧢", "timestamp": 1774839501}, {"author": "cryptoking7777777", "author_id": "1530812386", "id": "18385984411082380", "text": "🔥🔥🔥🔥", "timestamp": 1774400372}, {"author": "sumitk6893", "author_id": "47356449550", "id": "17938426125018147", "text": "Thank you", "timestamp": 1773768796}, {"author": "mazijade", "author_id": "13831989859", "id": "18132687184522675", "text": "Now imagine the colonial conditioning we were given as BIPOC children which shaped our sense of identities, emotions, our behaviours, and then our realities. Just food for thought.", "timestamp": 1773583203}, {"author": "fintechdailyclipsss", "author_id": "78668413738", "id": "18097506128007782", "text": "🙌🙌🔥", "timestamp": 1773378738}, {"author": "moodybooty1234", "author_id": "34560242064", "id": "18000831311885864", "text": "Help how do I shift my identity?", "timestamp": 1772686678}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.